  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CPiercing\uFF1E (When this Digimon attacks and deletes
    an opponent's Digimon, it performs any security checks it normally would.)[When
    Digivolving] You may trash up to 3 cards in your hand. If you do, for each card
    trashed, suspend 1 of your opponent's Digimon. Then, for each suspended Digimon
    your opponent has in play, gain 1 memory."
